[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1077","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1077.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1360","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 内核句柄处理本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 存在内核句柄处理缺陷，本地用户可通过用户态应用程序关闭已在内核态打开的文件句柄，当内核尝试关闭该句柄时由于双重释放导致系统崩溃，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者需拥有本地登录权限才能利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1360"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.473","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a (SP6a) 或更高版本，该版本修复了内核模式句柄在用户态关闭导致系统崩溃的问题。如无法升级，限制非授权用户本地登录系统作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q160/6/50.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7402.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1360.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1360","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1360.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1360.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-77p5-wxj2-c3mh/GHSA-77p5-wxj2-c3mh.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84461/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1360.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/4a6e09a063689f2d97734100478c1eef6f6dc387/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1077.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1078","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1078.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1362","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Win32k.sys 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 SP2 之前版本的 Win32k.sys 内核模块中存在参数校验缺陷，本地用户通过向特定 WIN32K 函数传递异常参数触发该漏洞，可导致系统内核崩溃引发拒绝服务。由于该漏洞需要本地访问权限且仅为 DoS 影响，危害等级较低。Microsoft 在 Windows NT 4.0 SP2 中修复了此问题。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1362"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.720","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 2 (SP2) 或更高版本，该补丁修复了 Win32k.sys 对畸形参数的处理缺陷。如无法升级，可通过限制本地用户对系统的交互式登录权限降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q160/6/01.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7403.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1362.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1362","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1362.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1362.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9j5c-5cw9-cqxv/GHSA-9j5c-5cw9-cqxv.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1362.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001038.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ac2f0f86-48c5-460b-a85e-14c08f2e58bf.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1078.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1079","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1079.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1363","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 3.51 及 4.0 系统中存在本地拒绝服务漏洞。本地用户可通过运行程序对同一文件创建大量锁，导致系统非分页池（NonPagedPool）资源耗尽，从而触发系统崩溃。该漏洞攻击前提为拥有本地登录权限，无法远程利用，影响范围限于 Windows NT 系列版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1363"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.840","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本系统（如 Windows 2000/XP），此漏洞在后续版本中已修复。对于无法升级的系统，可通过组策略限制非授信用户的本地交互式登录权限，降低攻击面。在注册表 `HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Session Manager\\Memory Management` 中调整 `NonPagedPoolSize` 值可缓解资源耗尽风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q163/1/43.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7405.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1363.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1363","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1363.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1363.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r2f7-pcrq-mgm9/GHSA-r2f7-pcrq-mgm9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84483/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1363.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-410.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1079.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1080","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1080.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1364","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 系统内核中存在本地拒绝服务漏洞，当本地用户通过 GetThreadContext 或 SetThreadContext 函数传入非法的内核模式地址时，系统未对输入指针进行有效验证，导致内核崩溃引发蓝屏。攻击者需具备本地登录权限且能够执行恶意程序方可利用，无法远程触发。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 所有版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1364"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:16.977","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 5 (SP5) 或更高版本（推荐 SP6a）即可修复此漏洞。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议迁移至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）。临时缓解措施：限制本地用户登录权限，仅允许受信任用户进行交互式登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q142/6/53.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7421.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1364.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1364","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1364.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1364.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h9g2-x4rf-46v3/GHSA-h9g2-x4rf-46v3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84476/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1364.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/4a6e09a063689f2d97734100478c1eef6f6dc387/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1080.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1094","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1094.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1382","title":"Novell NetWare NFS 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"NetWare NFS 模式 1 和 2 在实现 Unix \"只读\" 标志时存在权限许可漏洞。该漏洞源于系统将设置为 \"只读\" 的文件所有权更改为 root 用户，导致本地攻击者可通过创建 setuid 程序并将其标记为 \"只读\" 来利用此机制，NetWare-NFS 会自动将其转换为 root 所有的 setuid 程序，从而使攻击者获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Unix 平台上的 NetWare NFS 服务，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1382"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:19.213","remediation":"立即安装 Novell 官方补丁（TID 2940551），或升级 NetWare NFS 至不受影响的版本。如无法升级，应禁止普通用户在 NFS 共享目录中创建 setuid 文件，可在 exports 配置中添加 `nosuid` 挂载选项作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88427711321769&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90295697702474&w=2","http://support.novell.com/cgi-bin/search/tidfinder.cgi?2940551","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7246.php"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1094.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1105","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1105.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1444","title":"Alibaba genkey 交易明文发送漏洞","description":"Alibaba 2.0 的 genkey 密钥生成工具在生成 RSA 密钥对时错误地将私钥指数设置为 1，导致对应的公钥指数也为 1，使得 SSL 会话密钥以明文形式传输。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过网络嗅探窃取加密通信内容，或实施中间人攻击篡改数据。该漏洞影响 Alibaba 2.0 版本，且 Netscape Navigator 和 Internet Explorer 浏览器均不会对使用此类无效证书的 SSL 站点发出安全警告，进一步扩大了风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1444"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:27.233","remediation":"立即停止使用 Alibaba 2.0 的 genkey 工具生成密钥对，改用 OpenSSL 等标准工具生成 RSA 密钥（指数 e 至少为 65537）。如系统仍运行 Alibaba 2.0，应升级到支持安全密钥生成的版本或迁移至其他支持 TLS 加密的电子商务平台，避免交易数据以明文传输。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://catless.ncl.ac.uk/Risks/20.41.html#subj4","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1444.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1444","https://github.com/C2SP/wycheproof/blob/fc24cd5b787d8e496bff31b0468af693a652b0f2/doc/bib.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1444.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1444.json","https://github.com/huahua132/skynet_fly/blob/8d09dfdbf29612dbcc6b3acdcbede80434add9ef/3rd/openssl/wycheproof/doc/rsa.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-frc4-j6xj-vg8w/GHSA-frc4-j6xj-vg8w.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1444.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001044.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--600b6cd9-97c9-4150-9f4a-b4a83d5d1e48.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1105.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1107","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1107.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1451","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server 和 Site Server 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"IIS 4.0 及 Site Server 3.0 自带的 Winmsdp.exe 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过构造特制 HTTP 请求，利用该示例文件读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 平台上的 IIS 4.0 和 Site Server 3.0 版本，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1451"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.107","remediation":"删除 IIS 4.0 或 Site Server 3.0 服务器上的 Winmsdp.exe 示例文件（默认位于 /Msadc/Samples/Selector/ 目录），或升级到 IIS 5.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中禁用该示例目录的脚本执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q231/3/68.asp","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3271"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1107.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1110","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1110.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1452","title":"Microsoft Windows NT GINA 权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的 GINA（图形化标识与身份验证）组件存在权限许可和访问控制漏洞。具有物理访问权限的攻击者可在目标系统已锁定工作站的情况下，通过将剪贴板内容粘贴（CTRL-V）到用户名输入框中，从而泄露锁定用户剪贴板中的敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者需具备物理接触条件，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1452"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.233","remediation":"升级到 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统，这些版本已修复 GINA 在锁定状态下允许粘贴剪贴板内容的问题。如无法升级，可通过组策略禁用交互式登录前的粘贴功能，或确保物理访问环境受控，仅允许授权人员接触终端。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91788829326419&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91764169410814&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91822011021558&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q214/8/02.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/198","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1975"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1110.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1113","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1113.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1455","title":"Microsoft Windows NT RSH 访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows NT 3.5 至 4.0 版本中的 RSH 服务 (RSHSVC) 存在访问控制漏洞。当用户从已授权主机发起连接时，该服务未能正确解析 .Rhosts 文件中的访问控制规则，导致来自同一授权主机的未授权用户也可绕过身份验证访问 RSH 服务。远程攻击者可利用此漏洞在目标系统上以 SYSTEM 权限执行任意命令，影响 Windows NT 3.5/4.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1455"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.633","remediation":"建议立即禁用 Windows NT 系统中的 RSH 服务 (RSHSVC)，该服务已过时且存在严重访问控制缺陷。打开服务管理器，找到 \"RSHSVC\" 或 \"Remote Shell Service\"，将启动类型改为\"禁用\"并停止服务。如业务必须使用远程 shell，应迁移至 SSH 服务（如安装 OpenSSH for Windows），并配置防火墙规则阻止外部对 TCP 端口 514 的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q158/3/20.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7422"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1113.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1114","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1114.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1456","title":"thttpd HTTP服务器 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"thttpd HTTP 服务器 2.03 及更早版本存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送包含多个连续斜杠（/）的 GET 请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞源于对 URL 路径中斜杠字符的处理缺陷，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可能导致敏感信息泄露。受影响版本包括 thttpd 2.03 及之前所有版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1456"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.777","remediation":"升级 thttpd 至 2.04 或更高版本（2.04 版本修复了文件名解析中的路径遍历漏洞）。如无法升级，可在 Web 服务器前端（如反向代理或 WAF）配置规则，拦截包含多个连续斜杠（如 //）的 GET 请求路径作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.acme.com/software/thttpd/thttpd.html#releasenotes","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/10368","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1809"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1114.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1117","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1117.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1462","title":"Big Brother bb-hist.sh CGI History 模块远程文件泄露漏洞","description":"Big Brother 1.09b 及 1.09c 版本的 CGI History 模块（bb-hist.sh）存在远程文件泄露漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向该脚本发送特制请求，读取目标服务器上的任意文件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Big Brother 1.09b 和 1.09c 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。目前厂商已发布更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1462"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:29.523","remediation":"立即将 Big Brother 升级至 1.09d 或更高版本，该版本已修复 bb-hist.sh CGI 脚本中未正确限制文件读取路径的问题。如无法升级，可删除或禁用 CGI 目录下的 bb-hist.sh 脚本，并在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）配置中对 /cgi-bin/ 目录添加访问控制，仅允许授权 IP 访问。同时确保 CGI 脚本以低权限用户运行，限制其可读取的文件范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://bb4.com/README.CHANGES","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13440","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/142","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3755","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e6863af1ae3bb1cd8c56c1f1aac61d836661ac74/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1462.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1462","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1462.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1462.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/bb-hist.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fwqm-q5x9-cvjv/GHSA-fwqm-q5x9-cvjv.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/142/info.html","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0be18609-ef23-4332-9f03-c94852851693.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1117.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1119","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1119.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1465","title":"Cisco IOS 分布式快速交换访问控制列表安全绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 11.1 至 11.3 版本中启用了分布式快速交换（DFS）功能的路由器存在访问控制列表绕过漏洞。当路由器将流量从启用了 DFS 的入站接口交换到具有逻辑子接口的出站接口时，远程攻击者可利用此缺陷绕过 ACL 访问控制列表的过滤规则，导致未授权网络流量进入受保护网络段。该漏洞影响 Cisco IOS 11.1-11.3 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。Cisco 已发布安全公告并提供修复建议。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1465"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:29.897","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 11.3(6) 或更新版本以修复该漏洞。临时缓解措施：在接口配置模式下使用 `no ip route-cache distributed` 命令禁用分布式快速交换（DFS），或避免在启用了 DFS 的入站接口与逻辑子接口出站接口之间路由流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-016.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/iosdfsacl-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1401"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1119.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1123","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1123.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1473","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 页面重定向认证信息泄露漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 3.02 及 4.0 版本存在页面重定向认证信息泄露漏洞。当用户访问一个恶意网站时，该网站可将浏览器重定向至攻击者控制的第三方站点，而浏览器会自动将用户在原站点的认证信息（如 NTLM 凭据）发送给重定向目标站点，导致敏感认证信息泄露。攻击者无需特殊权限，仅需诱导用户访问恶意链接即可利用该漏洞。此漏洞影响范围广泛，可导致用户账户凭据被窃取。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1473"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:31.017","remediation":"立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.0 及以上版本，该漏洞已在 IE 5.0 中修复。对于无法升级的旧系统，可配置 IE 安全区域为「高」级别并禁用跨域访问自动传递凭据的选项。同时建议在代理服务器或网关层面过滤 HTTP Referer 头中的认证信息，防止重定向场景下凭据泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q176/6/97.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7426.php","http://www.osvdb.org/7818","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58a0ea900decdd7e971b95fcaa99234de5a5df5e/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1473.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1473","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1473.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1473.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rc82-f234-qr88/GHSA-rc82-f234-qr88.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1473.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001053.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--87310f6c-e3e3-44bc-9d56-f665a8c48b4b.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87907/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1123.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1125","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1125.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1476","title":"Intel Pentium 处理器拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Intel Pentium 处理器（MMX 和 Overdrive 型号）存在指令处理缺陷，本地攻击者可通过执行带有锁定前缀的非法 CMPXCHG8B 指令，导致处理器进入未定义状态，进而引发基于 Intel 的操作系统（如 Windows NT 和 Windows 95）挂起或崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用条件简单，攻击者仅需具备本地用户权限即可触发，无需特殊系统权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1476"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:31.403","remediation":"Windows NT 4.0 用户应安装 Service Pack 4 或更高版本（含 SP4 及后续更新），该补丁通过修改 HAL 层拦截无效指令传递至处理器。Windows NT 3.51 用户需安装微软提供的 pent-fix 热修复补丁，替换 Hal.dll 和 Ntkrnlmp.exe 等内核文件。Windows 95 无官方修复，建议升级至 Windows 98 或更高版本。如无法升级，可在应用层对 CMPXCHG8B 指令进行输入校验，阻止恶意程序执行该非法操作码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q163/8/52.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/704"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1125.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1128","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1128.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1481","title":"Squid Web Proxy 身份验证绕过漏洞","description":"Squid Web Proxy 2.2.STABLE5 及更早版本在使用外部认证机制时存在访问控制绕过漏洞。攻击者可在用户/密码对中插入换行符，绕过 Squid 的访问控制列表（ACL）检查，从而未经授权访问受保护的代理服务。该漏洞影响 Squid 1.0/1.1/2.1 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议升级至 Squid 2.2.STABLE6 或更高版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1481"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:32.043","remediation":"升级 Squid 至 2.2.STABLE6 或更高版本，该版本修复了外部认证时换行符绕过访问控制的问题。如无法升级，在外部认证脚本中对用户名和密码做换行符过滤（如 strip \\r\\n）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/33295","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/741","http://www.squid-cache.org/Versions/v2/2.2/bugs/","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3433","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19567","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58a0ea900decdd7e971b95fcaa99234de5a5df5e/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1481.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1481","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1481.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1481.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fx2h-93c2-339q/GHSA-fx2h-93c2-339q.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob